            She is consistently thorough in both understanding what I am hoping
            for with the treatment, and in answering any questions I may have.
            Her style of acupuncture is very gentle and restorative— I am so
            appreciative of her care, and recommend her to everyone!
          </p><p class="text-right font-bold mt-2">Molly D.</p>
        </div> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
